RATIONALE
================================================================================

This software is released under a Freedom License because:

1. CENSORSHIP RESISTANCE: Free speech requires free tools
2. KNOWLEDGE PRESERVATION: Information should be unstoppable
3. HUMAN RIGHTS: Privacy and communication are fundamental
4. INNOVATION: Open systems accelerate progress
5. EQUITY: No one should be priced out of participating

The internet was meant to be decentralized. This software helps restore that
vision by making every user into infrastructure.

