================================================================================
LEGAL POSITION
================================================================================

This software enables peer-to-peer communication. Like email, torrents, or
the web itself - it is neutral technology. Users are responsible for their
content and compliance with applicable laws.

We do not host content. We do not monitor users. We provide infrastructure
that is mathematically unstoppable because it has no center to attack.

If you use this for illegal purposes, that's on you, not the software or its
creators. The same way gun makers aren't liable for crimes, phone companies
aren't liable for phone scams, and car companies aren't liable for drunk driving.

This is a tool. A good tool. A free tool. Use it responsibly.

